text: thumb|Jan de Laval in 2011 Jan Patrik de Laval (28 March 1948 -- 19 December 2019) was a Swedish actor. He was born in Västrum, Sweden. He was known for his roles in Skilda världar and Rederiet. Laval died on 19 December 2019 in Stockholm at the age of 71. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Swedish movie actors Category:Swedish television actors
